The paper discusses Natural Language Processing (NLP) and the use of neural networks to tackle sequence to sequence (seq2seq) mapping problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions computer vision, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
